--------------
00. How to install Laravel 10 to any directory?
01. How to get the LIST of all installed packages along with the version in composer And CHECK WHY IT IS USED?
02. How can I REMOVE/UNINSTALL a package from Laravel using PHP Composer?

03. How to install Breez Authentication?
04. How to install Matwebsite Excel?
05. How to install Intervention Image?

06. How to install Harun IdGenerator?
07. How to install Laravel Permission Package?

---------------------------- Answer ---------------------

00_Ans:  How to install Laravel 10 to any directory
Prerequisites: PHP VERSION: 8.1 (minimum) and INSTALL: Composer, NPM.
CMD:- composer create-project laravel/laravel="10.10.*" Project_Folder_Name
TO RUN: php artisan serve

--------------

01_Ans: How to get the LIST of all installed packages along with the version in composer And CHECK WHY IT IS USED?
My-Install-Pack: php artisan package:discover --ansi
For All Pack: composer show
Check why it is used: composer why barryvdh/laravel-debugbar

-------------

02._Ans: How can I REMOVE/UNINSTALL a package from Laravel using PHP Composer?
composer remove realrashid/sweet-alert

-------------

03._Ans:  How to install Breez Authentication?
Website: https://www.educative.io/answers/how-to-install-a-breeze-laravel-authentication-package
CMD: composer require laravel/breeze --dev
     php artisan breeze:install
     php artisan migrate
     npm install
     npm run dev

-----------------------

04._Ans: How to install Matwebsite Excel?
Website: https://docs.laravel-excel.com/3.1/getting-started/installation.html
CMD: composer require maatwebsite/excel
Open Folder and ADD:- config/app.php
'providers' => [Maatwebsite\Excel\ExcelServiceProvider::class,]
'aliases' => ['Excel' => Maatwebsite\Excel\Facades\Excel::class,]

----------------

05._Ans: How to install Image Intervention?
Website: https://image.intervention.io/v2/introduction/installation
CMD: composer require intervention/image
Go to : config/app.php
'providers' => [ Intervention\Image\ImageServiceProvider::class ]
'aliases' => ['Image' => Intervention\Image\Facades\Image::class ]

---------06. How to install Harun IdGenerator?------------------
Web: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/49446329/laravel-generate-unique-order-number/58704860#58704860

INSTALL:
---------
composer require haruncpi/laravel-id-generator

TO USE in Controller for customized filed:
--------------------
use Haruncpi\LaravelIdGenerator\IdGenerator;
$prefix = date('Y');  
$emp_id = IdGenerator::generate(['table' => 'employees', 'field' => 'emp_id', 'length' => 8, 'prefix' =>$prefix]);

To Use in MODEL for  id:
------------------------
public static function boot(){
        parent::boot();
        self::creating(function ($model) {
            $model->order_number = IdGenerator::generate(['table' => 'orders', 'length' => 6, 'prefix' => date('y')]);
        });
    }

